---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Home
description: Gear advice from someone who learned the hard way. Trail stories from a farm kid who figured it out himself.
---

<section class="home-hero">
  <p class="hero-eyebrow">Est. 2026 · Mississippi · Hard-won opinions</p>
  <h1 class="hero-title">
    Gear advice from someone who <em>learned the hard way.</em>
  </h1>
  <p class="hero-body">
    No sponsored content. No gear I haven't thought hard about.
    Just stories from the trail — and what I'd carry today instead of what I carried then.
  </p>
  <a href="/stories/" class="hero-cta">Read the Stories →</a>
</section>

<div class="origin-strip">
  <p>
    <strong>The origin story:</strong> A church trip leader once handed me a cast iron skillet to carry into the backcountry.
    I swore I'd never let anyone pick my gear again. This site is what happened next.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <h2 class="section-title">Latest from the camp</h2>
    <a href="/stories/" class="section-link">All stories →</a>
  </div>

  {% set postslist = collections.posts %}
  {% if postslist.length %}

    {# Featured post - most recent #}
    {% set featured = postslist[0] %}
    <div class="post-featured">
      <div>
        <div class="post-card-tags">
          {% for tag in featured.data.tags %}
            {% if tag != "post" and tag != "posts" %}
              <span class="post-card-tag">{{ tag }}</span>
            {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
        <h3 class="post-card-title">
          <a href="{{ featured.url }}">{{ featured.data.title }}</a>
        </h3>
        {% if featured.data.description %}
          <p class="post-card-excerpt">{{ featured.data.description }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="post-card-meta">
          <time>{{ featured.date | readableDate }}</time>
        </div>
      </div>
      <span class="featured-label">Latest</span>
    </div>

    {# Rest of posts #}
    {% if postslist.length > 1 %}
      <div class="post-grid">
        {% for post in postslist | head(4) %}
          {% if loop.index > 1 %}
            <article class="post-card">
              <div class="post-card-body">
                <div class="post-card-tags">
                  {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
                    {% if tag != "post" and tag != "posts" %}
                      <span class="post-card-tag">{{ tag }}</span>
                    {% endif %}
                  {% endfor %}
                </div>
                <h3 class="post-card-title">
                  <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
                </h3>
                {% if post.data.description %}
                  <p class="post-card-excerpt">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
                {% endif %}
                <div class="post-card-meta">
                  <time>{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    {% endif %}

  {% else %}
    <p style="font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--smoke); font-style: italic; font-size: 0.85rem;">
      Stories coming soon. The campfire's just getting started.
    </p>
  {% endif %}
</div>
